| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2381 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 53a2cd1d-ac27-5e3e-aa6f-9815e294a128"
